Table oms.Shop2CarrierDO

Carrier naming as used by the shop instead of defaults.

Columns 

References[1] Column Type Constraints[2] Default Comment
id bigint PK, UNIQUE, NOT_NULL  
shopCarrierName varchar(50) The name of the carrier that should be used by the shop. Example "Deutsche Post DHL" 
CarrierDO carrierRef bigint NOT_NULL The carrier that should have a shop-specific naming. 
ShopDO shopRef bigint NOT_NULL The shop the carrier should be used for.
